For this analysis, I'll rename the files to use this naming convention:

> [feature]\_[interval]\_[src/sum]\_[shape].[filetype]

| Original                           | Updated                        |
|:-----------------------------------|:-------------------------------|
| dailyActivity_merged.csv           | activity_days_sum_wide.csv     |
| dailyCalories_merged.csv           | calories_days_sum_tall.csv     |
| dailyIntensities_merged.csv        | intensity_days_sum_wide.csv    |
| dailySteps_merged.csv              | steps_days_sum_tall.csv        |
| heartrate_seconds_merged.csv       | heartrate_seconds_src_tall.csv |
| hourlyCalories_merged.csv          | calories_hours_sum_tall.csv    |
| hourlyIntensities_merged.csv       | intensity_hours_sum_wide.csv   |
| hourlySteps_merged.csv             | steps_hours_sum_tall.csv       |
| minuteCaloriesNarrow_merged.csv    | calories_mins_src_tall.csv     |
| minuteCaloriesWide_merged.csv      | calories_mins_sum_wide.csv     |
| minuteIntensitiesNarrow_merged.csv | intensity_mins_src_tall.csv    |
| minuteIntensitiesWide_merged.csv   | intensity_mins_sum_wide.csv    |
| minuteMETsNarrow_merged.csv        | mets_minute_src_tall.csv       |
| minuteSleep_merged.csv             | sleep_mins_src_tall.csv        |
| minuteStepsNarrow_merged.csv       | steps_mins_src_tall.csv        |
| minuteStepsWide_merged.csv         | intensity_mins_sum_wide.csv    |
| sleepDay_merged.csv                | sleep_days_sum_wide.csv        |
| weightLogInfo_merged.csv           | bodycomp_logs_src_wide.csv     |